WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.069
(The following content may not be suitable for viewers under 15.)

2
00:00:04.069 --> 00:00:06.739
(Viewer discretion is advised.)

3
00:00:08.393 --> 00:00:11.194
There's nothing between me and Do Kyung.

4
00:00:12.233 --> 00:00:14.504
There has never been, and not even now.

5
00:00:14.504 --> 00:00:16.133
And that would never happen...

6
00:00:17.004 --> 00:00:18.234
even in the future.

7
00:00:18.434 --> 00:00:21.603
There's nothing I want from Do Kyung either.

8
00:00:22.874 --> 00:00:25.074
Especially, I'd never want to go back...

9
00:00:27.344 --> 00:00:28.844
to the Haesung family.

10
00:00:29.714 --> 00:00:30.754
What?

11
00:00:32.913 --> 00:00:34.354
I don't want that.

12
00:00:36.593 --> 00:00:37.954
You "don't want" that?

13
00:00:40.564 --> 00:00:42.693
I think I don't belong there.

14
00:00:43.733 --> 00:00:45.434
How dare you.

15
00:00:45.964 --> 00:00:47.934
It's better for me to stay away from your family,

16
00:00:49.364 --> 00:00:51.833
but I'm not that shameless...

17
00:00:52.634 --> 00:00:54.004
to hurt your family again.

18
00:00:55.704 --> 00:00:58.674
Then tell me where Do Kyung is. Where is he?

19
00:00:59.843 --> 00:01:01.083
I'm sorry,

20
00:01:01.513 --> 00:01:04.713
but I have no right to tell you that.

21
00:01:04.984 --> 00:01:07.624
Since I told you nothing is between him and me,

22
00:01:08.124 --> 00:01:10.993
it would be fair for me to tell you my thoughts only.

23
00:01:12.454 --> 00:01:13.663
Do you want me to believe...

24
00:01:14.424 --> 00:01:16.963
that Do Kyung likes you even though you don't?

25
00:01:17.094 --> 00:01:19.933
Why did you rush here when you heard I was here then?

26
00:01:21.264 --> 00:01:22.704
I work around this area.

27
00:01:23.433 --> 00:01:26.404
From what I heard, I thought it would be you.

28
00:01:27.174 --> 00:01:28.943
My curiosity got better of me.

29
00:01:28.943 --> 00:01:29.943
Of course,

30
00:01:29.943 --> 00:01:32.614
I wouldn't have come if I knew you were still here.

31
00:01:33.114 --> 00:01:36.514
I didn't want to have an uncomfortable meeting.

32
00:01:37.713 --> 00:01:40.154
You were planning to hide behind Do Kyung.

33
00:01:41.553 --> 00:01:42.954
That's not true.

34
00:01:43.693 --> 00:01:45.794
I already told you there's nothing between us.

35
00:01:46.094 --> 00:01:49.523
You know he left home because of you,

36
00:01:49.523 --> 00:01:51.734
so you probably know his number. However,

37
00:01:51.734 --> 00:01:53.963
you can't tell me where he is.

38
00:01:53.963 --> 00:01:55.963
Despite all this, there's nothing between you two?

39
00:01:58.374 --> 00:02:00.704
You don't want anything related to Haesung.

40
00:02:01.044 --> 00:02:03.014
You don't like my family.

41
00:02:03.713 --> 00:02:05.273
<v ->Is that what you mean? - Yes.</v>

42
00:02:08.283 --> 00:02:10.384
There's nothing I can do about your disbelief.

43
00:02:11.014 --> 00:02:13.724
But since I told you the truth about my feelings,

44
00:02:14.924 --> 00:02:16.753
I'd like to ask you not to visit my parents...

45
00:02:17.553 --> 00:02:21.724
regarding matters with Mr. Choi Do Kyung.

46
00:02:22.364 --> 00:02:24.993
<v ->Please don't. - Then send Do Kyung back.</v>

47
00:02:27.164 --> 00:02:28.833
If what you are telling me is the truth,

48
00:02:29.164 --> 00:02:31.974
send him back home now. Then I'll believe you.

49
00:02:31.974 --> 00:02:35.273
I believe that's out of my hands.

50
00:02:36.474 --> 00:02:39.313
It's his life. He will make his own decisions.

51
00:02:40.644 --> 00:02:43.213
I don't want to cross paths with you...

52
00:02:44.583 --> 00:02:46.924
for any matters regarding him.

53
00:02:48.854 --> 00:02:50.093
You...

54
00:02:51.123 --> 00:02:52.924
You are quite daring.

55
00:02:53.824 --> 00:02:55.093
I apologize.

56
00:02:55.123 --> 00:02:57.764
You didn't even ask how I knew he liked you.

57
00:02:59.634 --> 00:03:04.134
I'm aware that you always get your answers.

58
00:03:05.773 --> 00:03:09.713
Exactly. That's the power I have. Don't forget that.

59
00:03:11.243 --> 00:03:12.373
I won't.

60
00:03:13.484 --> 00:03:15.514
Tell Do Kyung to come see me.

61
00:03:17.053 --> 00:03:20.053
If I run into him, I will relay the message.

62
00:03:23.394 --> 00:03:25.523
Since I don't know what is going on inside your head,

63
00:03:25.894 --> 00:03:28.794
your claim of indifference means nothing.

64
00:03:31.394 --> 00:03:32.794
Don't you...

65
00:03:33.833 --> 00:03:36.164
dare dream about having Do Kyung, Ji An.

66
00:03:37.433 --> 00:03:38.803
I won't.

67
00:03:45.674 --> 00:03:47.313
If you finished what you meant to say to me,

68
00:03:48.114 --> 00:03:49.653
may I leave now?

69
00:04:28.183 --> 00:04:30.053
How could she be so bold?

70
00:04:46.873 --> 00:04:48.503
Are you all right, Ji An?

71
00:04:49.443 --> 00:04:51.643
You look pale.

72
00:04:53.714 --> 00:04:56.284
What happened? You said she left.

73
00:04:57.914 --> 00:04:59.654
I thought she did.

74
00:05:00.154 --> 00:05:01.854
She's no match for anyone.

75
00:05:05.053 --> 00:05:06.893
Ji An, you'll come over now?

76
00:05:11.734 --> 00:05:13.164
Ji An. Ji An...

77
00:05:15.563 --> 00:05:17.073
I guess I can wait.

78
00:05:27.183 --> 00:05:28.683
Two cups of Americano.

79
00:05:40.464 --> 00:05:43.594
Don't come now. She came back.

80
00:05:48.834 --> 00:05:49.834
(Hee)

81
00:05:49.834 --> 00:05:52.133
(Don't come now. She came back.)

82
00:05:54.174 --> 00:05:56.174
I didn't know since my phone was on silent mode.

83
00:05:57.513 --> 00:06:00.584
Do Kyung was the son of the Haesung family?

84
00:06:01.984 --> 00:06:03.854
She was one charismatic woman.

85
00:06:05.354 --> 00:06:07.253
What will you do now, Ji An?

86
00:06:08.984 --> 00:06:11.193
So that's why Hyuk...

87
00:06:11.724 --> 00:06:13.964
was so worried about you.

88
00:06:14.524 --> 00:06:17.594
Hee, don't tell Hyuk about this.

89
00:06:17.834 --> 00:06:19.234
I'll handle this by myself.

90
00:06:30.743 --> 00:06:32.873
I like the fact that you can manufacture...

91
00:06:32.873 --> 00:06:34.544
both injection and extrusion moldings.

92
00:06:34.943 --> 00:06:36.683
I will contact you after I discuss...

93
00:06:36.683 --> 00:06:39.154
the conditions of the production with the boss.

94
00:06:39.414 --> 00:06:41.953
We're short of work now, so we can take your order.

95
00:06:42.823 --> 00:06:45.193
Thank you. I'll wait for your call.

96
00:07:07.214 --> 00:07:08.484
It was Seo Ji An.

97
00:07:08.683 --> 00:07:10.654
The woman Do Kyung likes is Seo Ji An.

98
00:07:11.383 --> 00:07:13.024
How did you find that out?

99
00:07:13.683 --> 00:07:16.253
Thinking back, she was the only one in his life.

100
00:07:19.224 --> 00:07:21.263
Aren't you surprised?

101
00:07:22.224 --> 00:07:23.993
It's a relief if it's Seo Ji An.

102
00:07:24.164 --> 00:07:25.594
"It's a relief"?

103
00:07:25.993 --> 00:07:29.563
Dad might really disown him if it's Seo Ji An.

104
00:07:30.034 --> 00:07:31.534
He will be even more disappointed in us...

105
00:07:31.534 --> 00:07:34.643
for bringing her in and causing him to like her.

106
00:07:34.643 --> 00:07:36.174
That won't happen.

107
00:07:36.844 --> 00:07:39.174
Ji An won't let it get that far.

108
00:07:39.513 --> 00:07:41.614
How do you know that?

109
00:07:41.883 --> 00:07:44.614
She wasn't rude, and she was smart.

110
00:07:45.154 --> 00:07:47.284
She knows best how ill-fated...

111
00:07:47.284 --> 00:07:48.854
our families are.

112
00:07:49.623 --> 00:07:52.854
But she wouldn't tell us where he is.

113
00:07:53.294 --> 00:07:54.763
Did you meet with her?

114
00:07:55.664 --> 00:07:57.364
I just met her.

115
00:07:58.433 --> 00:08:00.364
I couldn't tell if she was smart...

116
00:08:00.563 --> 00:08:04.073
in an innocent way or trying to trick us.

117
00:08:05.933 --> 00:08:08.373
I couldn't read her thoughts.

118
00:08:08.844 --> 00:08:10.743
We'll find out once he comes back.

119
00:08:11.443 --> 00:08:14.544
She didn't even give me his number.

120
00:08:14.544 --> 00:08:16.614
She will tell him about your visit.

121
00:08:18.953 --> 00:08:20.284
She will, won't she?

122
00:08:21.654 --> 00:08:22.953
Even if she doesn't,

123
00:08:23.493 --> 00:08:26.424
you'll make sure Do Kyung comes back home.

124
00:08:38.334 --> 00:08:42.143
I don't know what's wrong with me

125
00:08:43.314 --> 00:08:46.444
Usually, this has to do with love. Who is she?

126
00:08:47.614 --> 00:08:48.814
<v ->Yong Gook. - Yes?</v>

127
00:08:49.913 --> 00:08:51.984
Ji Soo is acting strange all of a sudden.

128
00:08:52.954 --> 00:08:54.123
But...

129
00:08:54.653 --> 00:08:55.954
I'm acting strange too.

130
00:08:56.084 --> 00:08:58.824
No way. Did you find that out just now?

131
00:08:58.824 --> 00:09:00.564
It's been so long since you started to act weird.

132
00:09:01.824 --> 00:09:04.094
<v ->It's been going on long? - Yes.</v>

133
00:09:05.133 --> 00:09:06.503
You are confused, aren't you?

134
00:09:07.234 --> 00:09:10.633
"I decided to like Ji An a long time ago,"

135
00:09:10.773 --> 00:09:13.304
"but why do I keep thinking about Ji Soo?"

136
00:09:14.444 --> 00:09:17.673
On Christmas Eve, Ji An was inside,

137
00:09:17.673 --> 00:09:19.684
but you kept looking outside.

138
00:09:21.084 --> 00:09:22.543
You were waiting for her, right?

139
00:09:22.614 --> 00:09:24.954
Yes, that. That's it.

140
00:09:24.954 --> 00:09:29.084
When you met Ji An, you said it was fate.

141
00:09:29.084 --> 00:09:30.423
That was a load of nonsense.

142
00:09:30.523 --> 00:09:31.724
"Nonsense"?

143
00:09:31.724 --> 00:09:35.224
Why is that nonsense? She was my first love.

144
00:09:35.324 --> 00:09:37.834
Exactly. That. "First love".

145
00:09:37.893 --> 00:09:39.464
First love from 10 years ago.

146
00:09:40.503 --> 00:09:42.763
Do you think it's possible...

147
00:09:42.763 --> 00:09:45.273
to like someone after 10 years?

148
00:09:45.934 --> 00:09:49.743
You're caught under the idea of first love.

149
00:09:50.543 --> 00:09:52.074
"The idea of first love"?

150
00:09:52.214 --> 00:09:54.143
You and I are like brothers,

151
00:09:54.584 --> 00:09:56.614
but Do Kyung and I are estranged friends.

152
00:09:56.984 --> 00:09:59.253
If I thought that you really liked her,

153
00:09:59.253 --> 00:10:01.123
do you think I'd let him stay at the share house?

154
00:10:02.523 --> 00:10:04.194
He's the enemy of my brother.

155
00:10:04.954 --> 00:10:06.023
Yong Gook.

156
00:10:06.324 --> 00:10:07.763
You thought that far ahead?

157
00:10:07.824 --> 00:10:11.293
Besides, you knew Ji An likes Do Kyung.

158
00:10:11.493 --> 00:10:13.003
But you weren't jealous.

159
00:10:13.003 --> 00:10:14.464
You only worried about her...

160
00:10:14.763 --> 00:10:16.633
like a brother or an uncle.

161
00:10:17.434 --> 00:10:20.474
It's because what she went through is unimaginable.

162
00:10:21.173 --> 00:10:22.844
The girl you keep worrying about,

163
00:10:22.844 --> 00:10:24.513
and the girl you can't stop thinking about.

164
00:10:24.873 --> 00:10:26.074
Who do you think you are in love with?

165
00:10:28.043 --> 00:10:31.013
You've been worried about too many people.

166
00:10:32.954 --> 00:10:34.783
Stop pretending to take care of everybody.

167
00:10:35.184 --> 00:10:36.454
Even without you,

168
00:10:37.153 --> 00:10:39.354
they find their own ways when the right time comes.

169
00:10:40.623 --> 00:10:42.094
Have I been pretending?

170
00:10:43.734 --> 00:10:45.263
You've been the breadwinner...

171
00:10:45.263 --> 00:10:46.403
since you were young,

172
00:10:46.804 --> 00:10:48.263
and I liked you for your sense of responsibility.

173
00:10:48.263 --> 00:10:50.373
It's my sister. Just a moment.

174
00:10:52.533 --> 00:10:53.643
Yes, Hee.

175
00:10:53.804 --> 00:10:56.314
Hyuk, can you come to the cafe?

176
00:10:56.543 --> 00:10:59.373
Do Kyung's mother came to see Ji An.

177
00:10:59.373 --> 00:11:00.844
Do Kyung's mother?

178
00:11:02.783 --> 00:11:05.013
Did she say how she found out about it?

179
00:11:05.984 --> 00:11:07.584
She didn't say it,

180
00:11:07.883 --> 00:11:09.653
and Ji An didn't ask.

181
00:11:11.194 --> 00:11:12.393
But Hyuk,

182
00:11:13.094 --> 00:11:14.824
Do Kyung's mother...

183
00:11:15.023 --> 00:11:17.064
looked really feisty and scary.

184
00:11:17.564 --> 00:11:19.704
But Ji An was very calm.

185
00:11:21.033 --> 00:11:23.773
She knew she'd meet her one day.

186
00:11:24.673 --> 00:11:27.673
The day you brought Ji An to the house,

187
00:11:28.273 --> 00:11:30.074
she was all lethargic.

188
00:11:31.043 --> 00:11:33.314
It had something to do with her, didn't it?

189
00:11:35.283 --> 00:11:37.054
Was she...

190
00:11:38.114 --> 00:11:39.724
in a relationship with Do Kyung?

191
00:11:39.824 --> 00:11:41.023
That's not it.

192
00:11:42.224 --> 00:11:44.923
I can't tell you more about Ji An's business.

193
00:11:45.224 --> 00:11:46.464
Pretend you don't know.

194
00:11:46.623 --> 00:11:48.364
Don't ask Ji An questions.

195
00:11:48.623 --> 00:11:49.763
I won't.

196
00:11:50.393 --> 00:11:51.893
The same goes for you too.

197
00:11:52.834 --> 00:11:55.434
Ji An told me not to tell you.

198
00:11:55.934 --> 00:11:58.574
But I thought you should know.

199
00:12:01.474 --> 00:12:03.273
She doesn't want to bother me.

200
00:12:05.013 --> 00:12:07.684
(Waffle Restaurant Franchise Contract)

201
00:12:10.954 --> 00:12:13.224
Now, I am a businessman too.

202
00:12:14.984 --> 00:12:18.554
I will make it work out no matter what.

203
00:12:23.864 --> 00:12:25.464
Whatever business you want to run,

204
00:12:25.864 --> 00:12:27.934
you have to work at a similar business...

205
00:12:27.934 --> 00:12:29.163
for at least a year.

206
00:12:29.564 --> 00:12:33.074
Don't think about starting with a franchise.

207
00:12:35.743 --> 00:12:37.243
He's worried for no reason.

208
00:12:40.743 --> 00:12:43.184
Dad, what's wrong?

209
00:12:44.753 --> 00:12:46.484
Why... Why are you vomiting?

210
00:12:46.554 --> 00:12:47.554
It... It's nothing.

211
00:12:47.554 --> 00:12:50.493
I just drank coffee on an empty stomach.

212
00:12:51.554 --> 00:12:52.993
My gosh.

213
00:12:53.293 --> 00:12:55.793
He should've told me that he hadn't eaten.

214
00:13:16.584 --> 00:13:19.283
How much did you practice? You improved so quickly.

215
00:13:19.513 --> 00:13:22.153
I just did it to kill time.

216
00:13:22.153 --> 00:13:24.694
No way. I'm sure you used to play it before.

217
00:13:26.423 --> 00:13:28.663
It was a tree I couldn't climb...

218
00:13:29.094 --> 00:13:31.263
and a dream I couldn't dare to have.

219
00:13:31.663 --> 00:13:33.864
Everyone once had a dream, right?

220
00:13:34.503 --> 00:13:36.373
There are a lot of people like you.

221
00:13:36.373 --> 00:13:38.273
A lot of people learn to play an instrument...

222
00:13:38.273 --> 00:13:39.704
after they retire.

223
00:13:39.873 --> 00:13:41.704
I should introduce you to a hobby group.

224
00:13:41.704 --> 00:13:43.743
That's okay.

225
00:13:44.273 --> 00:13:46.243
Right. You said you were going somewhere.

226
00:13:46.243 --> 00:13:47.643
How long will you be gone for?

227
00:13:47.643 --> 00:13:49.684
You should come back when you're back.

228
00:13:52.584 --> 00:13:53.623
How could he vomit...

229
00:13:53.623 --> 00:13:56.554
after just a sip of coffee on an empty stomach?

230
00:13:57.393 --> 00:13:59.623
I think Dad is not well.

231
00:14:00.594 --> 00:14:02.464
Okay. I will ask him.

232
00:14:04.533 --> 00:14:06.334
I will call you. Okay.

233
00:14:11.133 --> 00:14:12.204
(Soo A)

234
00:14:12.204 --> 00:14:13.543
When are you getting off work?

235
00:14:16.413 --> 00:14:17.714
I can get off early.

236
00:14:34.793 --> 00:14:36.263
What's that?

237
00:14:37.094 --> 00:14:38.993
I packed in the morning and left.

238
00:14:39.763 --> 00:14:41.334
We can't keep on fighting...

239
00:14:41.834 --> 00:14:44.273
when your parents are around.

240
00:14:46.643 --> 00:14:48.574
I'll be staying at Seung Hun's place.

241
00:14:48.903 --> 00:14:49.974
What?

242
00:14:50.513 --> 00:14:51.814
Please tell your parents...

243
00:14:52.173 --> 00:14:54.614
that I had to go to a seminar.

244
00:14:57.084 --> 00:14:58.084
Soo A.

245
00:14:58.084 --> 00:14:59.383
If you come with me...

246
00:15:00.153 --> 00:15:01.954
to the hospital on the day of the surgery,

247
00:15:02.954 --> 00:15:04.694
we will be going home together.

248
00:15:05.594 --> 00:15:06.623
But if you don't come,

249
00:15:07.864 --> 00:15:09.163
I will consider the divorce paper signed.

250
00:15:09.163 --> 00:15:10.864
Did you even give it a thought?

251
00:15:11.094 --> 00:15:13.763
Did you hear the baby's heartbeat?

252
00:15:13.763 --> 00:15:15.564
I know that I am committing a sin.

253
00:15:16.434 --> 00:15:18.434
But a child is no toy.

254
00:15:18.734 --> 00:15:20.704
I have to give birth and raise that child.

255
00:15:20.704 --> 00:15:23.074
Nobody has the right to tell me what to do.

256
00:15:23.474 --> 00:15:26.143
Nobody has the right to tell me what to do...

257
00:15:27.184 --> 00:15:28.383
because this is my situation.

258
00:15:28.484 --> 00:15:31.214
So? Are you telling me...

259
00:15:32.184 --> 00:15:33.554
to choose between you and the baby?

260
00:15:35.623 --> 00:15:38.023
Think about why you didn't want to get married...

261
00:15:38.753 --> 00:15:40.824
or have a baby.

262
00:15:42.194 --> 00:15:43.834
Think about it once more.

263
00:15:46.934 --> 00:15:48.464
I will send you the booking confirmation.

264
00:15:49.834 --> 00:15:50.873
Take care.

265
00:16:39.554 --> 00:16:40.623
Ji An.

266
00:16:42.684 --> 00:16:43.753
Aren't you going home?

267
00:16:43.993 --> 00:16:45.653
We have to switch rooms today.

268
