415
00:25:21.074 --> 00:25:23.514
I have to bring out the bread. Bye.

416
00:25:41.923 --> 00:25:43.294
Aren't you going to the office today?

417
00:25:46.403 --> 00:25:48.104
I think Do Kyung will show up.

418
00:25:49.973 --> 00:25:51.504
He won't be able to come to the office,

419
00:25:51.504 --> 00:25:53.004
