I see.

538
00:32:21.564 --> 00:32:22.794
What...

539
00:32:23.633 --> 00:32:25.233
did you tell her?

540
00:32:27.703 --> 00:32:28.963
I don't think...

541
00:32:28.963 --> 00:32:31.433
she would've told you what I didn't say.

542
00:32:31.804 --> 00:32:33.544
She knew you'd ask me that like this.

543
00:32:34.574 --> 00:32:37.614
Then did you really say all that?

544
00:32:39.344 --> 00:32:40.943
There's nothing between you and me.

545
00:32:41.683 --> 00:32:43.213
And nothing will happen even in the future.

546
00:32:44.614 --> 00:32:46.114
Did you really have to say that?

547
00:32:48.524 --> 00:32:50.153
It's just how I feel.

548
00:32:50.693 --> 00:32:52.054
I told you before.

549
00:32:53.463 --> 00:32:54.963
It's not that I'm afraid.

550
00:32:55.963 --> 00:32:57.133
I don't like it.

551
00:32:57.693 --> 00:32:59.334
You live in a completely different world...

552
00:32:59.334 --> 00:33:00.703
where I don't belong.

553
00:33:01.233 --> 00:33:02.334
So...

554
00:33:04.203 --> 00:33:06.473
I don't want to go back there ever again.

555
00:33:06.673 --> 00:33:08.143
This is my decision.

556
00:33:08.744 --> 00:33:10.614
My decision for my own life.

557
00:33:11.044 --> 00:33:12.344
There's...

558
00:33:13.014 --> 00:33:15.244
another world that I can't see.

559
00:33:16.183 --> 00:33:17.483
It is...

560
00:33:18.354 --> 00:33:20.254
different from my world.

561
00:33:20.423 --> 00:33:21.453
I can't...

562
00:33:22.554 --> 00:33:24.594
be happy in that world.

563
00:33:27.594 --> 00:33:28.923
Couldn't you trust me...

564
00:33:28.923 --> 00:33:30.764
and pluck up your courage?

565
00:33:31.633 --> 00:33:33.304
You could've avoided it...

566
00:33:33.304 --> 00:33:34.334
by telling her...

567
00:33:34.663 --> 00:33:36.334
to ask me about everything.

568
00:33:38.004 --> 00:33:39.643
To ask you about it?

569
00:33:40.873 --> 00:33:42.304
What's that supposed to mean?

570
00:33:43.014 --> 00:33:45.143
That means I will accept you.

571
00:33:46.114 --> 00:33:47.713
I'm trying hard here.

572
00:33:48.143 --> 00:33:49.443
I'm trying real hard.

573
00:33:49.754 --> 00:33:50.953
I left home,

574
00:33:50.953 --> 00:33:52.314
and I'm trying to stand on my own feet.

575
00:33:52.314 --> 00:33:54.584
I'm doing all this because of you.

576
00:33:54.653 --> 00:33:56.854
Can't you see that? You know it.

577
00:33:57.123 --> 00:33:58.354
You know everything.

578
00:33:58.354 --> 00:34:00.064
I know. I really do.

579
00:34:01.824 --> 00:34:03.233
But I just can't understand this.

580
00:34:04.564 --> 00:34:06.463
If your heart is in the right place...

581
00:34:07.104 --> 00:34:09.503
and you're trying hard because of me,

582
00:34:10.434 --> 00:34:13.144
do I have to follow your wish? Why?

583
00:34:13.144 --> 00:34:14.704
Because you like me too.

584
00:34:15.574 --> 00:34:17.273
Because we're in the same place.

585
00:34:18.574 --> 00:34:21.383
I like you, but I won't do anything with you.

586
00:34:21.614 --> 00:34:24.483
I'm right here. Why can't you do that?

587
00:34:25.083 --> 00:34:27.253
I'm right here to protect you.

588
00:34:27.483 --> 00:34:29.693
I'm working hard to stand on my own feet...

589
00:34:29.693 --> 00:34:31.894
to be independent of my parents and grandfather.

590
00:34:32.923 --> 00:34:34.764
What do you want to do with me?

591
00:34:36.534 --> 00:34:38.293
Do you want to marry me?

592
00:34:38.894 --> 00:34:39.934
Yes.

593
00:34:41.264 --> 00:34:42.563
That's ridiculous.

594
00:34:44.103 --> 00:34:45.133
What?

595
00:34:45.434 --> 00:34:46.974
I said that's not what I want.

596
00:34:48.374 --> 00:34:50.313
I've been part of your family before.

597
00:34:50.673 --> 00:34:52.943
So I know the rules of your family.

598
00:34:53.744 --> 00:34:55.943
I know what they'd ask me for...

599
00:34:56.684 --> 00:34:59.184
and that I will have to obey those rules.

600
00:35:00.224 --> 00:35:01.583
That's not what I want.

601
00:35:01.653 --> 00:35:03.124
Why do you hate it so much?

602
00:35:03.724 --> 00:35:05.853
Because I'll have to live as someone who's not me.

603
00:35:06.894 --> 00:35:07.963
You told me that you don't...

604
00:35:07.963 --> 00:35:09.793
want to live as a part of the Haesung family.

605
00:35:10.063 --> 00:35:11.693
That's why you moved out to be independent

606
00:35:12.133 --> 00:35:13.133
I meant I'd be like that...

607
00:35:13.133 --> 00:35:14.534
if I went back without you.

608
00:35:15.304 --> 00:35:16.534
Things have changed now.

609
00:35:17.074 --> 00:35:19.844
Ji An, just take my hand.

610
00:35:20.074 --> 00:35:21.344
Please trust me.

611
00:35:21.344 --> 00:35:23.443
Why do I have to trust you?

612
00:35:24.514 --> 00:35:26.244
Do I have to take your hand...

613
00:35:26.244 --> 00:35:27.983
whenever you reach out?

614
00:35:27.983 --> 00:35:29.483
Why? Because you're rich?

615
00:35:30.483 --> 00:35:32.014
I don't need it.

616
00:35:32.083 --> 00:35:33.784
I don't like it because you're rich.

617
00:35:35.583 --> 00:35:36.653
I...

618
00:35:38.324 --> 00:35:40.124
just started to be happy only now.

619
00:35:41.063 --> 00:35:43.563
I just started to learn what it is like...

620
00:35:44.293 --> 00:35:46.603
to live at ease. Here. Now.

621
00:35:46.664 --> 00:35:48.833
Is your happiness cutting wood at a carpenter's?

622
00:35:48.934 --> 00:35:50.304
How would it make you happy?

623
00:35:51.534 --> 00:35:52.704
What did you say?

624
00:35:52.704 --> 00:35:54.903
You worked desperately to become a regular employee.

625
00:35:55.244 --> 00:35:56.974
I'm telling you that I will end that for you.

626
00:35:59.614 --> 00:36:01.414
Why are you upset with me?

627
00:36:01.713 --> 00:36:03.253
You don't have the right to be upset.

628
00:36:05.483 --> 00:36:07.054
Why would you think the poor...

629
00:36:07.054 --> 00:36:08.954
always have to listen to the rich?

630
00:36:11.853 --> 00:36:14.063
Do I not have the right to reject Haesung?

631
00:36:15.264 --> 00:36:17.394
Is it wrong to not like you because...

632
00:36:18.133 --> 00:36:19.534
you're the successor of Haesung?

633
00:36:22.733 --> 00:36:23.874
I did work hard...

634
00:36:23.874 --> 00:36:26.003
just to be a regular employee...

635
00:36:26.574 --> 00:36:27.844
in the past.

636
00:36:28.644 --> 00:36:29.813
But not anymore.

637
00:36:33.043 --> 00:36:34.213
I...

638
00:36:35.443 --> 00:36:37.383
have been through life and death.

639
00:36:38.313 --> 00:36:40.684
So I know it now. I know it.

640
00:36:42.523 --> 00:36:44.153
Where I belong,

641
00:36:44.353 --> 00:36:46.054
who I am,

642
00:36:46.693 --> 00:36:48.824
and where I can be happy.

643
00:36:52.394 --> 00:36:53.463
You...

644
00:36:55.233 --> 00:36:57.173
You're serious.

645
00:36:58.003 --> 00:36:59.273
Yes.

646
00:37:00.304 --> 00:37:01.403
I am.

647
00:37:04.443 --> 00:37:07.284
So please stop it, and go back.

648
00:37:08.844 --> 00:37:10.253
I keep feeling sorry,

649
00:37:11.153 --> 00:37:12.883
and it's hard to watch you struggle.

650
00:37:19.664 --> 00:37:21.364
I should get back to work.

651
00:38:34.204 --> 00:38:36.503
My name is Seo Tae Soo.

652
00:38:36.934 --> 00:38:38.574
I hope it won't happen,

653
00:38:38.574 --> 00:38:41.043
but if you find me collapsed on the floor,

654
00:38:41.144 --> 00:38:43.144
please call Hyangrim Hospital...

655
00:38:43.273 --> 00:38:46.443
or Ms. Yang Mi Jung.

656
00:38:49.483 --> 00:38:50.983
It's done now.

657
00:38:55.224 --> 00:38:56.423
Have a good day.

658
00:39:01.193 --> 00:39:03.164
(Overseas call)

659
00:39:06.963 --> 00:39:08.003
Hello?

660
00:39:08.034 --> 00:39:10.534
Ji Tae? This is Seok Doo.

661
00:39:10.804 --> 00:39:13.043
Hello, what's the matter?

662
00:39:16.003 --> 00:39:17.943
Dad is being odd?

663
00:39:18.043 --> 00:39:20.014
He has a stomachache and throws up often.

664
00:39:20.313 --> 00:39:23.284
He shows symptoms of stomach cancer.

665
00:39:23.353 --> 00:39:25.353
You should take him to the hospital.

666
00:39:25.383 --> 00:39:26.883
This doesn't feel good.

667
00:39:26.883 --> 00:39:28.684
Okay. I will.

668
00:39:30.494 --> 00:39:32.753
Thank you. Bye.

669
00:39:49.543 --> 00:39:50.644
Tae Soo.

670
00:39:56.883 --> 00:39:59.554
Tae Soo, what's wrong?

671
00:40:00.083 --> 00:40:01.883
You're breaking out in a cold sweat.

672
00:40:02.454 --> 00:40:04.153
What's the matter?

673
00:40:04.153 --> 00:40:06.563
I'm okay.

674
00:40:06.594 --> 00:40:08.364
You're not okay.

675
00:40:08.693 --> 00:40:11.333
I should call 911 and take you to the emergency room.

676
00:40:11.333 --> 00:40:14.304
No, you don't have to do that. My goodness.

677
00:40:14.333 --> 00:40:15.364
Never mind.

678
00:40:21.244 --> 00:40:24.414
Since it's for a family, I'll serve this one.

679
00:40:24.414 --> 00:40:25.414
Okay.

680
00:40:29.914 --> 00:40:31.353
Here's your order.

681
00:40:31.353 --> 00:40:33.724
<v ->It's our new menu. - It looks good.</v>

682
00:40:37.324 --> 00:40:38.693
How do you like it?

683
00:40:38.954 --> 00:40:41.664
The patty's made with beef only.

684
00:40:43.094 --> 00:40:44.864
It's moist and delicious.

685
00:40:45.693 --> 00:40:48.063
Honey, your parents would like this too.

686
00:40:48.063 --> 00:40:50.273
<v ->Let's bring them here. - Okay.</v>

687
00:41:09.054 --> 00:41:12.054
I didn't believe my husband when he said...

688
00:41:12.054 --> 00:41:14.624
Tae Soo showed symptoms of stomach cancer.

689
00:41:14.894 --> 00:41:17.463
But I found Tae Soo crouched outside the gate.

690
00:41:18.764 --> 00:41:21.264
I don't think it's something to ignore.

691
00:41:22.864 --> 00:41:24.804
He... He's showing Seok Doo's symptoms?

692
00:41:31.874 --> 00:41:34.043
My mom's full of energy.

693
00:41:35.443 --> 00:41:37.114
She's fine without me.

694
00:41:43.653 --> 00:41:44.853
Oh, I'm sorry.

695
00:41:45.793 --> 00:41:47.193
What? Mom...

696
00:41:55.503 --> 00:41:58.333
Why didn't she recognize me?

697
00:42:08.383 --> 00:42:10.784
He's taking guitar lessons and naps.

698
00:42:11.114 --> 00:42:12.184
It can't be.

699
00:42:18.423 --> 00:42:20.523
Did I sleep for that long?

700
00:42:26.704 --> 00:42:28.333
Ji Ho, you too?

701
00:42:28.934 --> 00:42:30.903
Why are you at home?

702
00:42:31.773 --> 00:42:34.144
Because of you. Sit down.

703
00:42:37.844 --> 00:42:39.144
What for?

704
00:42:39.684 --> 00:42:42.213
Seok Doo called me.

705
00:42:43.014 --> 00:42:44.153
Seok Doo called?

706
00:42:44.653 --> 00:42:45.883
What for?

707
00:42:46.253 --> 00:42:49.793
You've been vomiting and having stomach aches.

708
00:42:49.994 --> 00:42:51.994
He thinks they're stomach cancer symptoms,

709
00:42:51.994 --> 00:42:53.563
and he told us that you should see a doctor.

710
00:42:54.193 --> 00:42:55.864
Gosh, he must have lost his mind.

711
00:42:56.394 --> 00:42:58.733
Grandma died of stomach cancer too.

712
00:42:59.563 --> 00:43:01.003
It runs in the family.

713
00:43:01.463 --> 00:43:02.833
It wasn't just a few times.

714
00:43:02.974 --> 00:43:05.434
Ji Ho saw it and Mom noticed.

715
00:43:05.434 --> 00:43:06.974
And earlier, Hae Ja saw it too.

716
00:43:06.974 --> 00:43:10.173
He told you nonsense just to cause us trouble.

717
00:43:10.874 --> 00:43:13.043
It's not that. I'm fine.

718
00:43:13.514 --> 00:43:15.713
Let's go to the ER with us.

719
00:43:15.883 --> 00:43:18.583
I got a physical so I could board the ship.

720
00:43:18.883 --> 00:43:20.684
I just have stomach ulcers.

721
00:43:21.353 --> 00:43:23.054
You got a check-up?

722
00:43:23.394 --> 00:43:24.653
I did.

723
00:43:26.054 --> 00:43:28.923
Then show me the results.

724
00:43:30.164 --> 00:43:31.193
What?

725
00:43:31.193 --> 00:43:33.204
To see if the test was valid.

726
00:43:33.204 --> 00:43:36.603
Why would I show you what I got and checked?

727
00:43:36.833 --> 00:43:39.974
Then show it to me so I can look at it too.

728
00:43:39.974 --> 00:43:43.144
Why do you want to see my physical test results?

729
00:43:43.144 --> 00:43:44.874
Because we're worried.

730
00:43:45.644 --> 00:43:46.943
Why are you worried?

731
00:43:47.483 --> 00:43:48.914
Why do you care?

732
00:43:49.184 --> 00:43:52.983
I said I'm fine. What right do you have to ask?

733
00:43:53.483 --> 00:43:56.353
How could you say we don't have any rights?

734
00:43:56.353 --> 00:43:58.153
We're family.

735
00:43:58.153 --> 00:43:59.793
Why are we family?

736
00:44:00.164 --> 00:44:03.563
I told you before that we'll fend for ourselves.

737
00:44:04.333 --> 00:44:05.963
Stay out of my business.

738
00:44:08.034 --> 00:44:11.704
I won't ask you to pay for my medical bills, so stop.

739
00:44:11.704 --> 00:44:13.503
Don't say that.

740
00:44:13.644 --> 00:44:15.344
This is not about the hospital bills.

741
00:44:15.474 --> 00:44:16.974
Then what's the fuss?

742
00:44:17.114 --> 00:44:18.313
Dad.

743
00:44:18.713 --> 00:44:20.844
If you get so overly sensitive,

744
00:44:21.684 --> 00:44:23.184
it'll be too hard on us.

745
00:44:23.184 --> 00:44:24.353
Dad.

746
00:44:24.713 --> 00:44:27.753
Are you that angry that I considered emigrating...

747
00:44:27.753 --> 00:44:29.124
and moving out?

748
00:44:30.094 --> 00:44:33.693
I was disappointed and angry with you and Mom.

749
00:44:34.693 --> 00:44:36.023
Yes.

750
00:44:36.764 --> 00:44:40.333
Did it never occur to you to ask why we did that...

751
00:44:40.403 --> 00:44:44.233
and what we were thinking?

752
00:44:47.204 --> 00:44:48.574
If I were richer,

753
00:44:48.574 --> 00:44:51.813
not only would you have mentioned emigration,

754
00:44:52.374 --> 00:44:54.313
but you would've discussed with me.

755
00:44:56.313 --> 00:44:58.853
If I could've afforded your college tuition,

756
00:44:58.853 --> 00:45:01.724
would you not have told me before giving up?

757
00:45:02.483 --> 00:45:05.153
No, you wouldn't have even given up.

758
00:45:08.224 --> 00:45:09.523
Ji Tae.

759
00:45:10.264 --> 00:45:13.733
Do you know how cheerful and considerate you were?

760
00:45:15.034 --> 00:45:16.233
After the bankruptcy,

761
00:45:16.574 --> 00:45:19.574
you clammed up whenever you came home.

762
00:45:19.574 --> 00:45:22.644
You stopped smiling and didn't talk with me.

763
00:45:22.874 --> 00:45:24.213
You never made eye contact either.

764
00:45:25.014 --> 00:45:28.514
That was because I was still in shock.

765
00:45:30.054 --> 00:45:31.554
I know that.

766
00:45:32.983 --> 00:45:34.724
We went from being rich...

767
00:45:34.724 --> 00:45:36.824
to living in a small room in a day.

768
00:45:37.693 --> 00:45:39.793
How could you smile about that?

769
00:45:40.364 --> 00:45:42.764
You became worried about your future, annoyed,

770
00:45:43.063 --> 00:45:45.034
and hated me.

771
00:45:45.434 --> 00:45:46.534
I know.

772
00:45:47.133 --> 00:45:48.704
Then why complain?

773
00:45:49.164 --> 00:45:50.603
Just because I know...

774
00:45:51.534 --> 00:45:53.344
and understand you all...

775
00:45:54.344 --> 00:45:56.313
doesn't mean I didn't feel miserable.

776
00:45:58.773 --> 00:46:00.043
I felt terrible.

777
00:46:00.684 --> 00:46:02.443
I didn't know what to do.

778
00:46:02.583 --> 00:46:04.883
I felt terrible, but I didn't have the energy...

779
00:46:04.883 --> 00:46:06.653
to tell you not to worry.

780
00:46:07.423 --> 00:46:09.224
So I cowed around you.

781
00:46:09.583 --> 00:46:11.494
Ji Tae, Ji An, Ji Soo, Ji Ho,

782
00:46:12.494 --> 00:46:13.693
and you.

783
00:46:15.293 --> 00:46:17.034
I cowed around you.

784
00:46:17.693 --> 00:46:20.164
No one talked, discussed anything,

785
00:46:20.164 --> 00:46:21.833
or chatted with me.

786
00:46:22.764 --> 00:46:24.773
You all just smiled.

787
00:46:25.874 --> 00:46:28.644
I pretended not to care and smiled along.

788
00:46:29.603 --> 00:46:30.813
However,

789
00:46:31.773 --> 00:46:35.514
now, I'm sick of tiptoeing around you all the time.

790
00:46:38.014 --> 00:46:39.284
Now, I know...

791
00:46:39.983 --> 00:46:43.554
that I was a useless and meaningless father.

792
00:46:44.923 --> 00:46:46.664
And an untrustworthy husband.

793
00:46:48.494 --> 00:46:51.764
So I'm going to live my own life now.

794
00:46:52.233 --> 00:46:54.103
I'll make money on the fishing vessel...

795
00:46:54.103 --> 00:46:57.273
and do everything I wanted but couldn't do.

796
00:46:57.934 --> 00:47:00.043
So don't interfere with my life from now on.

797
00:47:00.903 --> 00:47:04.014
You have a way of shutting us up.

798
00:47:05.844 --> 00:47:07.313
Yes, that's it.

799
00:47:07.784 --> 00:47:09.213
That's what I want.

800
00:47:09.684 --> 00:47:11.784
Stay out of my business.

801
00:47:13.583 --> 00:47:15.483
Okay, fine.

802
00:47:26.034 --> 00:47:28.563
Can't he just show us the results?

803
00:47:51.494 --> 00:47:52.963
Will you really...

804
00:47:53.724 --> 00:47:55.494
stay angry until you leave?

805
00:47:56.293 --> 00:47:57.894
Why do I care?

806
00:47:58.563 --> 00:48:02.003
You mean nothing to me now.

807
00:48:04.603 --> 00:48:06.503
When a couple loses trust,

808
00:48:06.744 --> 00:48:08.574
we're as good as strangers.

809
00:48:10.344 --> 00:48:11.474
Honey.

810
00:48:12.414 --> 00:48:14.244
I said I'm sorry.

811
00:48:36.403 --> 00:48:38.534
When your dad refused to give me your number,

812
00:48:38.804 --> 00:48:40.043
I knew something was up.

813
00:48:40.903 --> 00:48:43.414
I want you to think about who you used to be...

814
00:48:43.773 --> 00:48:45.713
and what kind of person you once were.

815
00:48:45.974 --> 00:48:48.443
Just think about that once more.

816
00:48:48.943 --> 00:48:50.313
Only you can shine light...

817
00:48:50.583 --> 00:48:52.883
upon the road you wish to take.

818
00:48:53.583 --> 00:48:55.753
Why did he say that instead of saying...

819
00:48:56.454 --> 00:48:58.324
Ms. No had come over?

820
00:49:01.364 --> 00:49:03.534
(Contact List, Dad)

821
00:49:06.434 --> 00:49:08.633
The phone is turned off.

822
00:49:08.633 --> 00:49:10.974
Please leave a message after...

823
00:49:17.844 --> 00:49:21.383
Well, dad turned his phone off.

824
00:49:21.983 --> 00:49:23.983
Is he working now?

825
00:49:24.753 --> 00:49:26.583
I was wondering...

826
00:49:27.583 --> 00:49:29.583
if I should call you or not.

827
00:49:30.554 --> 00:49:31.894
Is something wrong?

828
00:49:38.633 --> 00:49:41.264
Close your mouth. You look like an idiot.

829
00:49:44.204 --> 00:49:45.704
It all makes sense now.

830
00:49:46.903 --> 00:49:48.974
Why you were fixated on Ji An.

831
00:49:50.043 --> 00:49:51.273
I found it odd.

832
00:49:52.644 --> 00:49:55.083
You met a few times by that car accident...

833
00:49:55.383 --> 00:49:56.954
and met again at work.

834
00:49:58.083 --> 00:50:01.454
I didn't think that was enough to fall in love.

835
00:50:03.753 --> 00:50:05.853
But there was much more to it.

836
00:50:06.894 --> 00:50:09.293
No wonder it was so messed up.

837
00:50:09.594 --> 00:50:11.534
It'll barely work even if we worked together...

838
00:50:11.864 --> 00:50:13.563
but Ji An won't cooperate.

839
00:50:13.864 --> 00:50:15.664
Her head's screwed on right.

840
00:50:15.934 --> 00:50:17.273
You're the crazy one.

841
00:50:18.103 --> 00:50:21.874
There's no way your family will accept her.

842
00:50:23.574 --> 00:50:26.313
She belongs to the creeps who stole their daughter.

843
00:50:26.313 --> 00:50:27.443
"Creeps"?

844
00:50:27.983 --> 00:50:29.514
Watch your language.

845
00:50:32.213 --> 00:50:33.423
This won't work out...

846
00:50:34.583 --> 00:50:37.824
unless you scratch your name off the family tree.

847
00:50:37.994 --> 00:50:40.764
But you won't do that, would you?

848
00:50:41.063 --> 00:50:42.764
I left without a penny.

849
00:50:42.764 --> 00:50:43.864
No.

850
00:50:44.133 --> 00:50:46.603
If you really turned your back on Haesung,

851
00:50:47.133 --> 00:50:48.704
why won't you spend your money?

852
00:50:49.534 --> 00:50:51.474
You got it when you started preschool.

853
00:50:51.474 --> 00:50:52.833
It's already yours.

854
00:50:53.003 --> 00:50:54.403
You won't spend it...

855
00:50:55.103 --> 00:50:57.273
because you're going to go back.

856
00:50:57.344 --> 00:50:59.344
You're sticking to the Haesung rules.

857
00:50:59.344 --> 00:51:01.483
Because I left to win over Ji An.

858
00:51:02.083 --> 00:51:03.353
Being independent...

859
00:51:03.353 --> 00:51:05.813
will free me from my grandpa and parents.

860
00:51:06.753 --> 00:51:08.253
Haesung can absorb...

861
00:51:08.253 --> 00:51:09.954
the company I started.

862
00:51:11.523 --> 00:51:13.063
It won't work like that.

863
00:51:13.364 --> 00:51:14.563
I can do it.

864
00:51:14.563 --> 00:51:15.894
The investment will come in today.

865
00:51:17.364 --> 00:51:19.133
Ji An's refusal is a bigger the problem.

866
00:51:19.364 --> 00:51:21.833
She refused? What did she refuse?

867
00:51:22.063 --> 00:51:24.173
She doesn't want to be part of Haesung.

868
00:51:25.003 --> 00:51:26.874
And she hates me because I'm from that family.

869
00:51:26.874 --> 00:51:27.903
What?

870
00:51:29.974 --> 00:51:32.574
She won't even look at what she can't have.

871
00:51:32.713 --> 00:51:33.813
No.

872
00:51:34.983 --> 00:51:37.713
She found what makes her happy in her situation.

873
00:51:37.753 --> 00:51:38.983
You believe that?

874
00:51:39.983 --> 00:51:41.583
What woman...

875
00:51:41.583 --> 00:51:44.094
would refuse to marry the heir of Haesung?

876
00:51:46.193 --> 00:51:47.923
She sounded serious.

877
00:51:48.624 --> 00:51:50.733
First, gain independence.

878
00:51:51.594 --> 00:51:53.804
Show her that you're able to stand...

879
00:51:53.804 --> 00:51:55.833
away from Mr. No and your mom.

880
00:51:56.164 --> 00:51:57.173
Then ask again...

881
00:51:57.503 --> 00:51:59.003
and see what she says.

882
00:52:00.173 --> 00:52:01.344
Would that work?

883
00:52:02.744 --> 00:52:04.014
Really?

884
00:52:04.014 --> 00:52:05.114
I'm sure about that.

885
00:52:05.414 --> 00:52:07.443
She doesn't trust you right now.

886
00:52:08.644 --> 00:52:09.713
What if...

887
00:52:10.454 --> 00:52:12.083
she's serious?

888
00:52:13.583 --> 00:52:15.653
What if she dislikes my heritage?

889
00:52:15.983 --> 00:52:17.353
Then it's over.

890
00:52:18.293 --> 00:52:19.693
There's no room to negotiate.

891
00:52:27.063 --> 00:52:29.304
You said things were favorable.

892
00:52:30.204 --> 00:52:31.633
What changed?

893
00:52:32.374 --> 00:52:33.804
We had a meeting and...

894
00:52:33.804 --> 00:52:36.204
the directors don't see the merit of investing.

895
00:52:36.374 --> 00:52:37.673
Goodbye then.

896
00:52:51.594 --> 00:52:52.923
(Paju factory)

897
00:52:54.824 --> 00:52:55.864
Hello.

898
00:52:55.864 --> 00:52:57.963
I don't think we can help you.

899
00:52:57.963 --> 00:53:00.733
But you said you're short of work...

900
00:53:01.003 --> 00:53:02.633
so the OEM would be possible.

901
00:53:05.474 --> 00:53:07.443
Your CEO said no?

902
00:53:23.894 --> 00:53:25.153
Yes, Choi Do Kyung speaking.

903
00:53:25.153 --> 00:53:28.164
I'm sorry. We dismissed your proposal.

904
00:53:28.193 --> 00:53:31.534
What? The audit process is over already?

905
00:53:48.114 --> 00:53:49.414
Grandpa?

906
00:53:54.653 --> 00:53:56.353
(Haesung Corporation)

907
00:53:56.954 --> 00:53:57.994
Yes.

908
00:54:00.164 --> 00:54:01.824
It's done already?

909
00:54:03.364 --> 00:54:04.434
Thanks.

910
00:54:10.403 --> 00:54:11.903
Do Kyung will return soon.

911
00:54:12.503 --> 00:54:15.003
He will? How?

912
00:54:15.503 --> 00:54:17.114
I broke his legs.

913
00:54:18.773 --> 00:54:21.344
He doesn't know he can't get away from me.

914
00:54:22.244 --> 00:54:24.713
He was raised to think he's special.

915
00:54:25.414 --> 00:54:27.224
He forgot he owes us.

916
00:54:35.164 --> 00:54:36.494
I lost my passbook.

917
00:54:36.494 --> 00:54:37.633
I need a new one.

918
00:54:37.633 --> 00:54:39.133
Okay. Just a moment.

919
00:54:39.864 --> 00:54:42.264
Fill in this form first.

920
00:54:50.914 --> 00:54:52.074
Are you going home?

921
00:54:52.474 --> 00:54:54.443
I'm going to see a client. I'll drop you off.

922
00:54:54.443 --> 00:54:56.454
Thanks. It's really cold.

923
00:55:22.204 --> 00:55:24.574
He's getting on fine with Ji An,

924
00:55:25.914 --> 00:55:28.614
but he complained that I dumped him?

925
00:55:31.184 --> 00:55:32.653
Was he toying with me?

926
00:55:42.764 --> 00:55:44.494
(Contact List, Ji Ho)

927
00:55:48.133 --> 00:55:50.804
Ji Ho, when's your day off?

928
00:56:19.963 --> 00:56:21.264
Dad.

929
00:56:25.534 --> 00:56:27.103
I'm home.

930
00:56:28.874 --> 00:56:29.874
What for?

931
00:56:29.874 --> 00:56:31.744
Don't even sit if you came here to nag me.

932
00:56:34.644 --> 00:56:36.784
Why is it nagging...

933
00:56:36.784 --> 00:56:38.583
if it's about your health?

934
00:56:39.353 --> 00:56:41.423
You don't need to get involved.

935
00:56:41.423 --> 00:56:43.324
I can manage my own health.

936
00:56:44.394 --> 00:56:46.293
Let me take you to a doctor tomorrow.

937
00:56:47.224 --> 00:56:48.293
What?

938
00:56:48.664 --> 00:56:50.133
The checkup you got...

939
00:56:50.133 --> 00:56:51.894
was from a small clinic.

940
00:56:51.894 --> 00:56:53.563
That's why you won't show the results.

941
00:56:54.864 --> 00:56:56.804
And you can't go deep-sea fishing.

942
00:56:57.233 --> 00:56:59.103
That's such hard work.

943
00:56:59.304 --> 00:57:00.943
I made up my mind.

944
00:57:00.943 --> 00:57:02.304
Don't bother me, and go.

945
00:57:04.443 --> 00:57:05.574
Dad.

946
00:57:06.784 --> 00:57:09.443
I'm really sorry.

947
00:57:09.713 --> 00:57:11.514
Stop being angry with me.

948
00:57:16.624 --> 00:57:18.554
Let's not talk about it anymore.

949
00:57:19.423 --> 00:57:21.824
You need to think about my circumstances too.

950
00:57:28.003 --> 00:57:29.133
Your "circumstances"?

951
00:57:29.903 --> 00:57:32.374
How we duped you into living with that family?

952
00:57:34.773 --> 00:57:35.943
I wasn't...

953
00:57:37.173 --> 00:57:40.514
able to face you after that.

954
00:57:42.244 --> 00:57:43.313
Is that so?

955
00:57:44.483 --> 00:57:46.824
It was in my situation.

956
00:57:47.784 --> 00:57:50.054
Why should I consider your situation?

957
00:57:50.724 --> 00:57:53.624
Did you ever tell me how you felt?

958
00:57:54.423 --> 00:57:55.693
After what you did,

959
00:57:55.693 --> 00:57:57.434
don't you dare pretend you care now.

960
00:57:58.764 --> 00:58:02.003
Did you think about it from my perspective?

961
00:58:03.434 --> 00:58:05.103
I did so many times.

962
00:58:05.673 --> 00:58:07.673
I felt terribly bad...

963
00:58:08.074 --> 00:58:10.144
for how I treated you when I left.

964
00:58:10.974 --> 00:58:13.344
Yes. You left.

965
00:58:14.014 --> 00:58:15.443
You left.

966
00:58:16.784 --> 00:58:20.124
I thought you'd say you wouldn't go.

967
00:58:20.724 --> 00:58:23.324
Even if you really were their daughter,

968
00:58:23.594 --> 00:58:25.994
I didn't think you'd say you'd go right away.

969
00:58:26.463 --> 00:58:28.793
You were my daughter for 28 years.

970
00:58:29.193 --> 00:58:32.364
It didn't take you a month or two, or even a week.

971
00:58:32.693 --> 00:58:36.304
Three days. That's all it took for you to say yes.

972
00:58:37.773 --> 00:58:40.874
You left while blaming me for being poor.

973
00:58:43.414 --> 00:58:45.644
I first met you to talk you out of it.

974
00:58:45.874 --> 00:58:48.313
To say that it's not you, and that you shouldn't go.

975
00:58:49.583 --> 00:58:51.114
You already made up your mind,

976
00:58:51.114 --> 00:58:53.023
but I didn't want to hurt you,

977
00:58:53.253 --> 00:58:54.624
so I kept asking...

978
00:58:55.653 --> 00:58:57.793
if you were leaving because of...

979
00:58:57.793 --> 00:58:59.594
what your mom had done.

980
00:59:00.563 --> 00:59:01.624
I thought...

981
00:59:02.264 --> 00:59:03.934
you have made up your mind...

982
00:59:03.934 --> 00:59:05.733
in a hurry for our sake.

983
00:59:07.063 --> 00:59:08.434
Ji An.

984
00:59:09.903 --> 00:59:10.974
You can't...

985
00:59:12.173 --> 00:59:13.543
go there.

986
00:59:14.503 --> 00:59:15.543
I'm sorry...

987
00:59:16.514 --> 00:59:17.773
for all...

988
00:59:18.043 --> 00:59:20.144
the tough times you went through.

989
00:59:20.614 --> 00:59:22.483
It's about what you want.

990
00:59:22.943 --> 00:59:24.554
That's what counts.

991
00:59:25.583 --> 00:59:27.624
I... I want to know what you're thinking.

992
00:59:27.624 --> 00:59:30.653
If they say you don't have to move in,

993
00:59:31.353 --> 00:59:32.753
will you stay here?

994
00:59:33.824 --> 00:59:36.224
I wanted to hear you say you had no choice.

995
00:59:37.063 --> 00:59:39.333
Only then, would you be less perplexed...

996
00:59:39.664 --> 00:59:41.563
even if I told you the truth,

997
00:59:42.103 --> 00:59:43.103
Yes.

998
00:59:44.173 --> 00:59:45.434
I want to go.

999
00:59:46.574 --> 00:59:48.644
I struggled so much until now.

1000
00:59:48.744 --> 00:59:50.014
I wanted to die every day.

1001
00:59:50.014 --> 00:59:51.874
My efforts alone wouldn't cut it.

1002
00:59:51.874 --> 00:59:54.813
Why did you pick me up in the first place?

1003
00:59:55.844 --> 00:59:57.684
I never thought...

1004
00:59:57.914 --> 00:59:59.923
that I'd hear my own daughter say...

1005
00:59:59.923 --> 01:00:01.724
she wanted to die.

1006
01:00:03.423 --> 01:00:05.554
I looked into your eyes,

1007
01:00:06.253 --> 01:00:07.923
and I couldn't speak.

1008
01:00:08.793 --> 01:00:11.193
You asked me why I'd adopted you.

1009
01:00:11.894 --> 01:00:13.304
I needed to say...

1010
01:00:13.304 --> 01:00:15.304
it was Ji Soo and not you.

1011
01:00:16.434 --> 01:00:17.974
But my mouth froze...

1012
01:00:18.434 --> 01:00:20.273
and my heart stopped.

1013
01:00:21.144 --> 01:00:22.804
I couldn't move...

1014
01:00:24.014 --> 01:00:25.673
as if I was having a nightmare.

1015
01:00:27.983 --> 01:00:29.383
I'm sorry.

1016
01:00:30.554 --> 01:00:31.614
No.

1017
01:00:32.083 --> 01:00:34.523
It's possible for you to do that.

1018
01:00:35.253 --> 01:00:37.594
You must've struggled so much.

1019
01:00:38.153 --> 01:00:40.624
So I'm sorry...

1020
01:00:40.994 --> 01:00:42.324
and sorry again.

1021
01:00:43.094 --> 01:00:44.164
But...

1022
01:00:44.963 --> 01:00:47.164
it's not fine for me.

1023
01:00:47.903 --> 01:00:51.133
I was rejected by my own daughter.

1024
01:00:51.574 --> 01:00:54.804
Even when you realized it was Ji Soo,

1025
01:00:54.804 --> 01:00:56.173
you didn't come look for me.

1026
01:00:57.114 --> 01:00:59.514
"Dad, I'm in trouble."

1027
01:01:00.184 --> 01:01:03.353
That's what you and Ji Tae always said...

1028
01:01:05.114 --> 01:01:07.054
when I was still competent.

1029
01:01:08.883 --> 01:01:10.293
Dad.

1030
01:01:12.153 --> 01:01:15.693
You made me realize that I'm a useless dad,

1031
01:01:15.864 --> 01:01:17.364
and I've realized it.

1032
01:01:17.864 --> 01:01:18.934
So...

1033
01:01:19.764 --> 01:01:21.633
leave me alone now.

1034
01:01:22.733 --> 01:01:24.034
I'm sorry.

1035
01:01:24.074 --> 01:01:25.974
Don't say that anymore.

1036
01:01:27.574 --> 01:01:28.874
I don't need it.

1037
01:01:29.304 --> 01:01:30.914
I don't want it anymore.

1038
01:01:31.543 --> 01:01:32.673
You guys.

1039
01:02:32.474 --> 01:02:33.673
I'm sick...

1040
01:02:34.903 --> 01:02:36.414
of living like this.

1041
01:02:37.543 --> 01:02:40.083
People ignore me and despise me.

1042
01:02:40.514 --> 01:02:43.353
Living a miserable and servile life.

1043
01:02:44.253 --> 01:02:45.983
I can't take it anymore. No.

1044
01:02:47.454 --> 01:02:49.124
Why do you not want me to go?

1045
01:02:49.324 --> 01:02:52.293
Why did you pick me up in the first place?

1046
01:03:39.003 --> 01:03:41.943
Why are you waiting here? Someone might follow you.

1047
01:03:44.744 --> 01:03:46.014
Are you that scared?

1048
01:04:00.693 --> 01:04:03.594
I am. I'm very terrified.

1049
01:04:05.063 --> 01:04:06.563
So what are you going to do for me?

1050
01:04:12.233 --> 01:04:13.503
I'll ask you only one question.

1051
01:04:14.673 --> 01:04:15.943
Please answer it.

1052
01:04:18.673 --> 01:04:20.014
Do you...

1053
01:04:21.043 --> 01:04:22.313
really mean that?

1054
01:04:24.153 --> 01:04:26.284
If you really meant it when you said...

1055
01:04:28.153 --> 01:04:29.454
that I must not be the son of Haesung Corporation,

1056
01:04:30.253 --> 01:04:31.293
I'll...

1057
01:04:32.653 --> 01:04:34.224
stop now.

1058
01:04:38.994 --> 01:04:40.333
Answer me.

1059
01:04:44.204 --> 01:04:45.434
I really meant it.

1060
01:04:45.574 --> 01:04:46.704
Then...

1061
01:04:47.744 --> 01:04:48.744
let's stop this.

1062
01:04:50.443 --> 01:04:51.744
If you really meant it,

1063
01:04:54.114 --> 01:04:55.784
I can't help it.

1064
01:04:57.684 --> 01:04:59.083
Even if I die,

1065
01:05:00.753 --> 01:05:02.994
I'll still be the son of Haesung Corporation.

1066
01:05:10.563 --> 01:05:11.764
However,

1067
01:05:12.833 --> 01:05:14.103
you must remember this.

1068
01:05:15.664 --> 01:05:16.773
When I say...

1069
01:05:18.204 --> 01:05:19.903
I won't do something, I really mean it.

1070
01:05:22.074 --> 01:05:23.313
Like you said,

1071
01:05:24.644 --> 01:05:27.344
I can't stop being myself for you.

1072
01:05:30.554 --> 01:05:31.684
Okay.

1073
01:05:35.224 --> 01:05:36.954
I'll give you one last chance.

1074
01:05:38.994 --> 01:05:40.124
Don't let me go.

1075
01:05:57.713 --> 01:05:58.943
Then it's over.

1076
01:06:00.014 --> 01:06:01.244
Goodbye.

1077
01:06:47.164 --> 01:06:49.633
(My Golden Life)

1078
01:06:51.994 --> 01:06:53.733
Why are you so hard to get?

1079
01:06:54.403 --> 01:06:56.264
Act like you're my boyfriend.

1080
01:06:56.264 --> 01:06:58.233
Hi. He's my boyfriend.

1081
01:07:00.074 --> 01:07:01.173
We need to talk.

1082
01:07:01.403 --> 01:07:03.043
Do Kyung will be home soon.

1083
01:07:03.043 --> 01:07:05.374
Father blocked all of Do Kyung's investments.

1084
01:07:05.374 --> 01:07:07.784
I don't want to live as a horse on Grandpa's chess.

1085
01:07:07.883 --> 01:07:09.483
How did it go with Ji An?

1086
01:07:09.483 --> 01:07:10.753
I'll try to hate her.

1087
01:07:10.914 --> 01:07:13.353
